						<p><hi rend="bold">Koṅgu, Sundara-Pāṇḍya, Year 28 = c. 14th century.</hi></p>						

						<p>Mutilated and stones out of order. Records the gift of one achchu for a lamp to the temple of Attāṇīśvaramuḍaiyār by a member of Veḷḷāḷan Padaittalaikaḷ clan. [This reading is from two different slabs in between which are built two more slabs containing fragmentary inscriptions.]</p>						

